New contract (preferred): update project status for a specific WO + SubProjectId.
Payload contract:
{
  "_request": {
    "WOList": [
      {
        "Company": "425",
        "SubProjectId": "425-P0000001-00001",
        "WorkOrderGUID": "{...}",
        "WorkOrderID": "...",
        "Status": 5|6
      }
    ]
  }
}
